title: Is Bobby Returning To Dancing With The Stars? + Listener Gets COVID-19 Vaccine + Mike D’s Epic Cheat Day Menu
itunes:title: Is Bobby Returning To Dancing With The Stars? + Listener Gets COVID-19 Vaccine + Mike D’s Epic Cheat Day Menu
description:
Eddie asks Bobby about his Instagram from the other day where he mentioned he’d be returning to 'Dancing With The Stars'. Bobby won the show two years ago and then claimed to be retired from dance...but will he actually return!? We talk to listener Sarah who just received the COVID-19 vaccine. She answers all of our questions. Plus, Mike D reveals what he will be eating for his annual “Christmas Purge” meal!
